      </follow-up>
      <follow-up wave="C5+" task="future">
        Add integration tests in UniversalIngestParameterizationTests.cs (path mentioned
        in POML §outputs) covering: PracticeAreaHint routing to per-area prompts (depends
        on D2/031); CostCapOverride affecting Phase 2 cost-gating (depends on Phase 2
