        changing the gate decision boundary (verifiable after C4 wires the playbook).
        Integration tests are blocked on C4; this task delivered the unit-test surface
        instead, which is the appropriate STANDARD-rigor scope.
      </follow-up>
    </follow-ups>
    <quality-gates>
      STANDARD rigor — Step 9.5 quality gates (code-review + adr-check) skipped per
